    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a complete VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under high torque loads. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission is paired with a recently replaced clutch and a factory-spec limited-slip differential, providing crisp engagement and linear power delivery. The suspension geometry remains tight with upgraded polyurethane bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the drivetrain and cooling system are optimized for peak thermal efficiency and performance.",
