    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and utility. The exterior presents beautifully with a high-gloss finish; while there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch, the body is straight and free of any major dents. Inside, the cabin is a testament to careful ownership. The leather seats are plush and well-preserved, showing only light bolstering wear on the driver\u2019s side, and the dashboard remains free of any sun damage or cracks. All electronic features, including the dual-zone climate control, heated seats, and the infotainment system, are fully operational. Mechanically, this car is in its prime. It has been serviced every 5,000 miles with full synthetic oil, and the brakes and tires were replaced within the last year. The engine starts instantly with no odd noises, and the transmission delivers smooth, confident shifts across all gears. This is a solid, honest car that has many years of reliable service left to offer.",
      "price": 34500.0,
