      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the S54B32 atmospheric inline-six, renowned for its 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. The high-pressure Double VANOS system has been recently calibrated for optimal cam phasing, ensuring a linear power band. Power is sent to the rear wheels through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a functional M-Variable limited-slip differential. Critically, the rear subframe mounting points have been inspected and reinforced, addressing the chassis' primary structural fatigue point. The suspension retains its factory-spec kinematics with refreshed bushings and aluminum control arms for precise turn-in. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina consistent with a well-loved enthusiast vehicle, the mechanical vitals remain robust and track-ready.",
